and creating change.

00:30:39.940 --> 00:30:42.790
The cover of the book is
a poem about thresholds.

00:30:42.790 --> 00:30:45.650
"Marking passage, the
framework of conception,

00:30:45.650 --> 00:30:48.510
on the verge of where the
end becomes the beginning.

00:30:48.510 --> 00:30:51.670
The shape like a doorway to open."

00:30:51.670 --> 00:30:54.510
The form and content of this
book are closely related,

00:30:54.510 --> 00:30:56.390
relying on each other for meaning.

00:30:56.390 --> 00:31:00.520
I used a Turkish map fold, so when
the book opens, Daphne's hand opens

00:31:00.520 --> 00:31:04.620
in the midst of leafing
and reaching for the sky.

00:31:04.620 --> 00:31:08.390
In Ovid's Metamorphoses, we read
the nymph Daphne's passion was

00:31:08.390 --> 00:31:10.940
to run free in the forest and hunt.

00:31:10.940 --> 00:31:12.980
Then she becomes hunted herself.

00:31:12.980 --> 00:31:15.860
she flees to escape
being ravaged by Apollo.

00:31:15.860 --> 00:31:19.290
