into a tree rooted forever in place.

00:31:24.210 --> 00:31:27.370
I read many translations
of this tale,

00:31:27.370 --> 00:31:29.870
but I couldn't figure
out why a tree?

00:31:29.870 --> 00:31:33.190
I do love trees, but it didn't
seem an apt metamorphoses

00:31:33.190 --> 00:31:35.340
for someone like Daphne.

00:31:35.340 --> 00:31:39.820
So, for this book, I wrote
my own version of this story.

00:31:39.820 --> 00:31:42.700
Her determination to
remain free is inspiring,

00:31:42.700 --> 00:31:45.920
yet her call for change
has an unexpected outcome,

00:31:45.920 --> 00:31:49.280
as do many thresholds we cross.

00:31:49.280 --> 00:31:51.580
The reader is asked to
put the book in motion,

00:31:51.580 --> 00:31:54.160
